y from october  until may  prior to october  he had served as regional president for the southeast region since may  read more mr lukemire was named president and chief operating officer of the company in february  he served as executive vice president and chief operating officer of the company from december  until february  prior to this appointment mr lukemire had served as executive vice president north american operations of the company from april  until december  as executive vice president business execution of the company from may  until april  and as president us consumer regions of the company from october  until may  prior to october  he had served as regional president for the southeast region since may  source the scotts miraclegro company on    sign up for equilar atlas and view michael c lukemires full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like michael c lukemire more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in michael c lukemires network and community follow changes in michael c lukemires employment and moneyinmotion connect with michael c lukemire through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example michael c lukemire michael c lukemires connections  sign up now to view michael c lukemires  connections » lawrence a hilsheimer executive vice president and chief financial officer greif inc arnold w donald dir president and chief executive officer carnival stephanie m shern board member gamestop corp alan h barry former president and chief operating officer masco corporation michael p kelty former evp the scotts miraclegro company james f mccann executive chairman of the board flowerscom inc john r vines board member the scotts miraclegro company claude l lopez former evp international and cmo the scotts miraclegro company vincent c brockman former executive vice president  general counsel corporate secretary